+ Class Methods

++ Public

* Solar_View::__call() -- Executes a helper method with arbitrary parameters.

* Solar_View::__construct() -- Constructor.

* Solar_View::__set() -- Disallows setting of underscore-prefixed variables.

* Solar_View::addHelperClass() -- Add to the helper directory path stack.

* Solar_View::addTemplatePath() -- Add to the template directory path stack.

* Solar_View::assign() -- Sets variables for the view.

* Solar_View::display() -- Displays a template directly.

* Solar_View::escape() -- Built-in helper for escaping output.

* Solar_View::fetch() -- Fetches template output.

* Solar_View::getHelper() -- Returns an internal helper object; creates it as needed.

* Solar_View::getHelperClass() -- Returns the helper class stack.

* Solar_View::getTemplatePath() -- Returns the template directory path stack.

* Solar_View::newHelper() -- Creates a new standalone helper object.

* Solar_View::partial() -- Executes a partial template in its own scope, optionally with 
variables into its within its scope.

* Solar_View::setHelperClass() -- Reset the helper class stack.

* Solar_View::setTemplatePath() -- Reset the template directory path stack.

* Solar_View::template() -- Returns the path to the requested template script.

Inherited Methods:

